Project Rules

Project name: Bun Theory by Bakar & Roast

Architecture:

Frontend

* NextJS
* shadcn UI

Backend

* NestJS
* Prisma
* PostgreSQL

Rules:

* Backend must expose REST APIs.
* Frontend must call backend via services layer.
* Admin routes require authentication.
* Customer routes are public.

Main Features:

Customer

* View menu
* Place order
* Choose pickup or delivery

Admin

* Manage menu
* View orders
* Update order status
* Limit max orders per day

Notifications

* WhatsApp message to admin when order is placed
* WhatsApp message to customer when order status changes

